snippet.title: Pale Abyss || Official Pre-Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a journey into the depths of the Pale Abyss, discover the many secrets within and perhaps... you can even bring back what was stolen?

For more information check out our Steam page!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3451290/Pale_Abyss/

Or join our Official Discord Server!
https://discord.gg/dACH8G3EaH
